2. How often should I visit Code Hair Ladies Salon for hair styling services?
The frequency of your visits will depend on your individual hair care needs and styling preferences. For most clients, we recommend scheduling appointments every 4-6 weeks to maintain your desired look and keep your hair in optimal condition.

3. Can I book a consultation before scheduling a hair styling appointment?
Absolutely! We offer complimentary consultations to all our clients to discuss their hair goals, assess their hair type and condition, and provide personalized recommendations. Book your consultation today and let our expert stylists guide you towards achieving your dream hair.
